<tt xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml" xmlns:amll="http://www.example.com/ns/amll" xmlns:itunes="http://music.apple.com/lyric-ttml-internal" xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" xmlns:tts="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#styling" itunes:timing="Word" xml:lang="ja"><head><metadata><ttm:agent type="person" xml:id="v1"/><ttm:agent type="other" xml:id="v2"/><amll:meta key="musicName" value="Just Be Friends (feat. 小豆沢こはね)"/><amll:meta key="musicName" value="Just Be Friends"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="小豆沢 こはね"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="小豆沢こはね"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="あずさわ こはね"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="アズサワ コハネ"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="Azusawa Kohane"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="小豆沢心羽"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="小豆澤心羽"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="小豆泽心羽"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="아즈사와 코하네"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="Vivid BAD SQUAD"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="ビビッドバッドスクワッド"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="Bibiddo Baddo Sukuwaddo"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="炫狂小队"/><amll:meta key="album" value="Vivid BAD SQUAD Another Vocal Album"/><amll:meta key="album" value="プロジェクトセカイ カラフルステージ！ feat. 初音ミク　アナザーボーカルアルバム Vivid BAD SQUAD"/><amll:meta key="album" value="Project SEKAI COLORFUL STAGE! feat. Hatsune Miku Another Vocal Album Vivid BAD SQUAD"/><amll:meta key="ncmMusicId" value="2623126895"/><amll:meta key="qqMusicId" value="001Fin9T0DTYZk"/><amll:meta key="qqMusicId" value="570385803"/><amll:meta key="spotifyId" value="4YlwHOYYgGB3ZosuZXCEeE"/><amll:meta key="appleMusicId" value="1803088773"/><amll:meta key="isrc" value="JPX302467060"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithub" value="68000793"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithubLogin" value="ranhengzhang"/><iTunesMetadata xmlns="http://music.apple.com/lyric-ttml-internal"><translations><translation type="subtitle" xml:lang="en"><text for="L5">It came to mind in the early morning yesterday</text><text for="L6">As if I gathered broken pieces of glass</text><text for="L7">What the heck is this? A drop from a cut on my finger</text><text for="L8">Is this what we really hoped for?</text><text for="L9">I knew it at the bottom of my heart</text><text for="L10">That the hardest choice would be the best</text><text for="L11">My self-love refuses it and repeats self-contradiction</text><text for="L12">When can I tell it to you?</text><text for="L13">In this slowly decaying world</text><text for="L14">I&apos;m struggling but it&apos;s the only way</text><text for="L15">Carving your faded smiles, I pulled out the plug</text><text for="L16">I screamed with my hoarse voice</text><text for="L17">Rebound and resonance echo in vain</text><text for="L18">Nothing is left behind at the end</text><text for="L19">Of the me that has been unchained</text><text for="L20">The coincidences that we&apos;d piled up</text><text for="L21">Degenerate into the dark and are broken in pieces</text><text for="L22">&quot;No matter what we do, life is just like that.&quot;</text><text for="L23">I mumbled as somebody&apos;s tears flow down the dried cheeks</text><text for="L28">Yesterday a tranquil night made me realize</text><text for="L29">It&apos;d be useless to pick up fallen petals</text><text for="L30">Because it&apos;d never bloom again, it&apos;s tiny but already dead on my palms</text><text for="L31">Our time stopped long ago</text><text for="L32">I remember the season we first met</text><text for="L33">And your graceful smile</text><text for="L34">Bringing up old issues, we hurt each other as badly as possible</text><text for="L35">Our hearts are full of thorns</text><text for="L36">With this continuous dull relationship</text><text for="L37">Grievously I can&apos;t change my mind</text><text for="L38">I still love you, I don&apos;t wanna be apart from you, but I have to tell you</text><text for="L39">It&apos;s raining heavily in my mind, I&apos;m stunned,</text><text for="L40">I&apos;m standing dead, my vision is blurry</text><text for="L41">Despite my determination,</text><text for="L42">The pain is still penetrating</text><text for="L43">The bond between us had come apart</text><text for="L44">And is dying away in everyday</text><text for="L45">Goodbye, my sweetheart, it&apos;s over</text><text for="L46">We had to leave without turning back</text><text for="L47">Just once, just once, if I could have my wish to come true</text><text for="L48">I&apos;d be born again and again, and go see you on those days</text><text for="L49">I screamed with my hoarse voice</text><text for="L50">Rebound and resonance echo in vain</text><text for="L51">Nothing is left behind at the end</text><text for="L52">Of the me that has been unchained</text><text for="L53">The bond between us had come apart</text><text for="L54">And is dying away in everyday</text><text for="L55">Goodbye, my sweetheart, it&apos;s over</text><text for="L56">We had to leave without turning back</text><text for="L57">It&apos;s all over</text></translation><translation type="subtitle" xml:lang="zh-Hans"><text for="L1">保持朋友关系 这是我们唯一能做的</text><text for="L2">保持朋友关系 是时候说再见了</text><text for="L3">保持朋友关系 这是我们唯一能做的</text><text for="L4">保持朋友关系……</text><text for="L5">脑中浮现 昨天一大早</text><text for="L6">好像是在收拾打破的玻璃碎片的情景</text><text for="L7">这到底是什么情况？ 被割伤的手指滴下了血滴</text><text for="L8">我们真的干了这种蠢事吗？</text><text for="L9">我很清楚 在心底深处</text><text for="L10">最难过的选择才是最佳答案</text><text for="L11">不断抗拒的是自我保护 和自我矛盾的无限循环</text><text for="L12">我什么时候才说的出口呢？</text><text for="L13">慢慢腐朽的这个世界</text><text for="L14">不断挣扎的我只剩一条活路</text><text for="L15">将你褪色的微笑 刻划在我心中 然后拔掉忍耐的栓子</text><text for="L16">喊叫到声嘶力竭</text><text for="L17">反响 残响 空虚地响着</text><text for="L18">就算把锁给解开</text><text for="L19">也什么都不会留下</text><text for="L20">两人相遇的偶然</text><text for="L21">暗转 断线 无尽虚幻</text><text for="L22">“反正就是这样啦” 如此低语</text><text for="L23">流在毫无生气的脸庞上的 是谁的眼泪</text><text for="L24">这是我们唯一能做的</text><text for="L25">保持朋友关系 是时候说再见了</text><text for="L26">保持朋友关系 这是我们唯一能做的</text><text for="L27">保持朋友关系 保持朋友关系 保持朋友关系……</text><text for="L28">我才发现 在昨晚风雨停息过后</text><text for="L29">就算把掉在地上的花瓣给捡起来</text><text for="L30">它再也无法绽放 掌心这微小的死亡</text><text for="L31">让我们两人的时间就此停滞</text><text for="L32">我想起了 我们初次相遇的季节</text><text for="L33">你那温柔笑着的脸庞</text><text for="L34">就把现在变成过去 两人遍体鳞伤</text><text for="L35">我们的内心已满是荆棘般的尖刺</text><text for="L36">面对沉重苦闷的这段感情</text><text for="L37">令人悲伤的是我这不曾变过的心</text><text for="L38">明明是如此深爱 没办法轻易分开 但我不说出口不行</text><text for="L39">下在心里的倾盆大雨</text><text for="L40">呆然 竦然 让视线都模糊</text><text for="L41">虽说早已做好觉悟 那份痛楚</text><text for="L42">仍贯穿了我的身体</text><text for="L43">连结两人的羁绊</text><text for="L44">剪断 解开 消失在日常生活中</text><text for="L45">再见了曾深爱的人 到此为止了</text><text for="L46">别再回头就向前走吧</text><text for="L47">一次就好 一次就好 愿望可以实现的话</text><text for="L48">不管要转世几次 我都会去找寻那时候的你</text><text for="L49">喊叫到声嘶力竭</text><text for="L50">反响 残响 空虚地响着</text><text for="L51">就算把锁给解开</text><text for="L52">也什么都不会留下</text><text for="L53">连结两人的羁绊</text><text for="L54">剪断 解开 消失在日常生活中</text><text for="L55">再见了曾深爱的人 到此为止了</text><text for="L56">别再回头就向前走吧</text><text for="L57">就此划下句点了</text><text for="L58">保持朋友关系 是时候说再见了</text><text for="L59">保持朋友关系 这是我们唯一能做的</text><text for="L60">保持朋友关系 是时候说再见了</text><text for="L61">保持朋友关系</text><text for="L62">保持朋友关系 这是我们唯一能做的</text><text for="L63">保持朋友关系</text><text for="L64">保持朋友关系 是时候说再见了</text><text for="L65">保持朋友关系</text><text for="L66">保持朋友关系 这是我们唯一能做的</text><text for="L67">我们本该 早该如此</text><text for="L68">保持朋友关系 是时候说再见了</text><text for="L69">我们本该 做普通朋友</text><text for="L70">保持朋友关系</text><text for="L71">保持朋友关系</text></translation></translations><songwriters><songwriter>Dixie Flatline</songwriter></songwriters><transliterations><transliteration xml:lang="ja-Latn"><text for="L5"><span begin="35.870" end="36.000" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">u</span> <span begin="36.000" end="36.160" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">ka</span><span begin="36.160" end="36.280" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">n</span> <span begin="36.280" end="36.500" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">da</span><span